{"id":160840,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bear_Behaving_Badly","text":"\"Bear Behaving Badly\" is a children's comedy television programme. It is shown at 17:45 on Thursday evenings. It stars Barney Harewood and Nev the Bear both from the \"ex\" CBBC programme \"SMILE\". It is produced by Darrall Macqueen Limited for CBBC.\nThe programme also includes characters such as Allyson Brown as Beatrice (Beetroot, as Nev calls her), Glen Davis as Mr. Andy Prank (Mr. Angry-pants, as Nev calls him), and Beverly Hills as Postie. The puppets are Nev The Bear (Ross Mullan) and Crazy Keith (Simon Buckley)","categories":[],"infobox_types":["Television"],"annotations":[{"uri":"Child","surface_form":"child","offset":27},{"uri":"Comedy","surface_form":"comedy","offset":38},{"uri":"Television_programme","surface_form":"television programme","offset":45},{"uri":"Barney_Harewood","surface_form":"Barney Harewood","offset":119},{"uri":"Nev_the_Bear","surface_form":"Nev the Bear","offset":139},{"uri":"CBBC","surface_form":"CBBC","offset":171},{"uri":"SMILE","surface_form":"SMILE","offset":187},{"uri":"Producer","surface_form":"produced","offset":201},{"uri":"Darrall_Macqueen_Limited","surface_form":"Darrall Macqueen Limited","offset":213},{"uri":"CBBC","surface_form":"CBBC","offset":242},{"uri":"Fictional_character","surface_form":"characters","offset":276},{"uri":"Allyson_Brown","surface_form":"Allyson Brown","offset":295},{"uri":"Beatrice","surface_form":"Beatrice","offset":312},{"uri":"Glen_Davis","surface_form":"Glen Davis","offset":351},{"uri":"Prank","surface_form":"Prank","offset":374},{"uri":"Beverly_Hills","surface_form":"Beverly Hills","offset":421},{"uri":"Puppet","surface_form":"puppet","offset":450},{"uri":"Ross_Mullan","surface_form":"Ross Mullan","offset":476},{"uri":"Crazy_Keith","surface_form":"Crazy Keith","offset":493},{"uri":"Simon_Buckley","surface_form":"Simon Buckley","offset":506}]}